name: Temple of the Kings
desc: You can activate 1 Trap Card the turn it was Set. You can send 1 "Mystical Beast of Serket" in your Monster Zone and this card you control to the Graveyard; Special Summon 1 monster from your hand or Deck, or 1 Fusion Monster from your Extra Deck. You can only use each effect of "Temple of the Kings" once per turn.

ocg.pack: Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Monsters VI: Expert 2 Game Guide 1 promotional card
